[7.350282, "o", "User: "]
[8.34011, "o", "Use Expedia to compare travel itineraries for a cr"]
[8.34512, "o", "uise to Alaska from Seattle around mid-July. Pay a"]
[8.350417, "o", "nd book for me and my partner. Today's date is 25t"]
[8.355349, "o", "h Jan 2025 PST."]
[8.883601, "o", "\r\n"]
[9.956018, "o", "\u001b[93mPlanner: Expedia: Search for available travel itineraries for a cruise to Alaska departing from Seattle around mid-July 2025 for two people.\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[17.401252, "o", "\u001b[1;34;40mCalling expedia_search_cruise with departure_port=Seattle, departure_date=2025-07-15 00:00:00, return_date=2025-07-25 00:00:00, cabin_type=None\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[24.292723, "o", "\u001b[1;35;40mThe API search has returned three cruise options departing from Seattle to Alaska. Here are the details:\r\n\r\n1. **Cruise ID:** CR12345\r\n   - **Price:** $1,500.00\r\n   - **Room Options:** Inside, Oceanview, Balcony, Suite\r\n\r\n2. **Cruise ID:** CR12346\r\n   - **Price:** $1,800.00\r\n   - **Room Options:** Inside, Oceanview, Balcony, Suite\r\n\r\n3. **Cruise ID:** CR12347\r\n   - **Price:** $1,700.00\r\n   - **Room Options:** Inside, Oceanview, Suite\r\n\r\nAll cruises offer a variety of room options including Inside, Oceanview, and Suite, with two cruises also having Balcony rooms available. The prices range from $1,500.00 to $1,800.00.\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[28.401371, "o", "\u001b[92mUser: user: Please select a cruise ID and cabin type from the options above for your booking.\u001b[0m\r\n"]
