[40.152704, "o", "\u001b[1;34;40mCalling expedia_get_cruise_info with cruise_id=CR12346\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[52.6259, "o", "\u001b[1;35;40mEmbark on an enchanting 7-night Alaskan cruise aboard CR12346 starting June 15, 2024, departing from Seattle. Experience the serene beauty of Alaska with port visits to Juneau, Skagway, the breathtaking Glacier Bay National Park, and Ketchikan, plus two days at sea for relaxation.\r\n\r\n**Key Highlights:**\r\n- **Departure & Return:** Seattle, Washington\r\n- **Duration:** 7 nights \r\n- **Itenary Summary:**\r\n  - **Day 1:** Depart Seattle at 4:00 PM\r\n  - **Day 3:** Explore Juneau from 9:00 AM to 8:00 PM\r\n  - **Day 4:** Discover Skagway from 7:00 AM to 6:00 PM\r\n  - **Day 5:** Cruise through Glacier Bay from 6:00 AM to 5:00 PM\r\n  - **Day 6:** Visit Ketchikan from 8:00 AM to 5:00 PM\r\n  - **Day 8:** Arrive back in Seattle by 7:00 AM\r\n\r\n**Amenities & Services:**\r\n- Complimentary WiFi and all-inclusive meals\r\n- Enjoy a variety of onboard entertainment\r\n- Relax and rejuvenate in the swimming pool, spa, and fitness center\r\n- Children's club for younger cruisers\r\n\r\n**Dining Options:**\r\n- Main Dining Room, specialty restaurants, buffet, and room service\r\n\r\nThis cruise is currently available for booking, offering an enriching adventure through the majestic landscapes of Alaska while providing ample comfort and amenities onboard.\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[59.296685, "o", "\u001b[92mUser: user: Would you like to proceed with the booking of this cruise for 2 guests? \u001b[0m\r\n"]
