[71.458937, "o", "\u001b[1;34;40mCalling expedia_get_cruise_addons with cruise_id=CR12346\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[78.558799, "o", "\u001b[1;35;40mFor Cruise ID CR12346, a variety of optional add-ons are available to enhance your cruise experience. These include:\r\n\r\n1. **Travel Insurance**: Ensure peace of mind with comprehensive coverage for trip cancellations and medical emergencies, priced at $100.00.\r\n\r\n2. **Honeymoon Package**: Perfect for newlyweds, this package offers amenities like a bottle of champagne and chocolate-covered strawberries, available for $150.00.\r\n\r\n3. **Wi-Fi Package Upgrade**: Enjoy unlimited high-speed internet throughout your cruise for $80.00.\r\n\r\n4. **Dining Experience Package**: Delight in gourmet dining every night with access to our specialty restaurant, costing $200.00.\r\n\r\n5. **Spa Package**: Relax with exclusive spa treatments and sessions, available for $175.00.\r\n\r\n6. **Photography Package**: Capture special moments with a professional photographer, including a personal photo shoot, for $120.00.\r\n\r\nThese add-ons can be enjoyed for the entire duration of your cruise, allowing you to tailor your journey to your preferences.\u001b[0m\r\n"]
