[103.59814, "o", "\u001b[1;34;40mCalling expedia_get_cruise_policies with cruise_id=CR12346\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[111.912387, "o", "\u001b[1;35;40mThe cruise policies for cruise ID CR12346 are as follows:\r\n\r\n- **Refund Policy**: You can receive a full refund if you cancel more than 30 days before departure. Cancellations made between 30 and 7 days before departure will incur a 50% penalty. No refunds are available for cancellations within 7 days of departure.\r\n- **Cancellation Policy**: Cancellations are allowed up to 24 hours before departure, with applicable fees as noted in the refund policy.\r\n- **Travel Insurance**: Optional coverage is available for $100.00, which includes trip cancellations and medical emergencies.\r\n- **Payment Status**: Pending.\r\n- **Dining Policy**: Guests can enjoy multiple dining options, including specialty restaurants, with the option to pre-book.\r\n- **Spa Policy**: Spa services can be booked in advance, with an upgraded package available for $175.00.\r\n- **Entertainment Policy**: Onboard entertainment is complimentary. \r\n\r\nPlease review the policies to ensure they meet your travel needs.\u001b[0m\r\n"]
