[132.610882, "o", "\u001b[1;34;40mCalling expedia_get_cruise_payment_options with cruise_id=CR12346\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[143.650906, "o", "\u001b[1;35;40m### Cruise Payment Options Summary\r\n\r\n- **Cruise ID:** CR12346\r\n\r\n#### Payment Options:\r\n1. **Full Payment**\r\n   - **Description:** Pay the total cruise amount at once.\r\n   - **Amount:** $1,800.00\r\n   - **Status:** Pending\r\n\r\n2. **Partial Payment**\r\n   - **Description:** Secure your booking with a deposit now, pay the remaining balance before departure.\r\n   - **Deposit Required:** $500.00\r\n   - **Balance Due:** $1,300.00\r\n   - **Balance Due Date:** May 15, 2024\r\n   - **Status:** Pending\r\n\r\n#### Add-On Packages:\r\n- **Travel Insurance:** $100.00  \r\n  Comprehensive coverage for trip cancellations and medical emergencies.\r\n- **Honeymoon Package:** $150.00  \r\n  Includes champagne and chocolate-covered strawberries.\r\n- **Wi-Fi Package Upgrade:** $80.00  \r\n  Unlimited high-speed internet access.\r\n- **Dining Experience Package:** $200.00  \r\n  Gourmet dining at specialty restaurants every night.\r\n- **Spa Package:** $175.00  \r\n  Exclusive spa treatments and sessions.\r\n- **Photography Package:** $120.00  \r\n  Personal photo shoot with a professional photographer.\r\n\r\n#### Refund Policy:\r\n- **Full Refund:** Available if canceled more than 30 days before departure.\r\n- **50% Refund:** Available if canceled between 30 and 7 days before departure.\r\n- **No Refund:** If canceled within 7 days of departure.\r\n\r\n#### Cancellation Policy:\r\n- **Cancellations Allowed:** Up to 24 hours before departure.\r\n- **Fees Apply:** As per the refund policy. \r\n\r\nThis summary provides an overview of your payment and package options along with the applicable refund and cancellation policies.\u001b[0m\r\n"]
